node.text: So happy to be an Ambassador for @vivolife 🌸 I have been using their products for yearssss now since they started up as a small business till today when they're doing SO INCREDIBLY WELL 👏🏼 I was so excited when they approched me to be an Ambassador because I truly use and love them! I use the protein shake the most (salted caramel YUM)  but they are a fully plant based company that provides errrrythung you need for workout performance and just keeping yourself feeling and looking cute 😂🙌🏾 as well as the products being extremely thought out and delicious I also appreciate their sustainability efforts AND that with every order a tree is planted 💛 USE CODE RADHI10 For 10% OFF YOUR ORDER 🌸💛stay tuned imma be sharing recipes and all sorts xxx

node.text: @womenofimpact ROUND 3!!! (link to full video in my bio) !!!! This is the third time my sweet friend @lisabilyeu and I have sat down to avaaa chat. And I am always just so shocked after because we get into such a beautiful flow we have healthy debate we discuss things and unpack them deeply. I love her so much and I really hope this conversation is useful in some way. It's almost like a therapy session for me, say things I didn't intend to felt things I didn't know I needed to.  It was CLEANSING 😂😂😅😅

node.text: Anyone got a cute cry face tutorial?🤦🏽‍♀️🤷🏻‍♀️ LISTENNN this was not how it was supposed to go..BUT THAS THE WAY IT WENT. But also sending anyone away from their family so much love..We got this 💛💛

node.text: REMINDER: Don’t let that ONE bad thing that happened today ruin your mood for the rest of the day!  We tend to focus on the pain and forget the joys of life so easily. Let’s change that 💛

node.text: Love when big brands like @nike show up with sustainable lines 😍🌱! The recycled polyester comes from recycled plastic bottles cleaned shredded and blended with yarn to make these cute outfits! Recycled polyester reduces carbon emissions by 30% compared to virgin polyester. Also just in terms of comfort, super soft super flexible and reallllly cute colors. We've got a long way to go but all these little changes collectively do a whole lot of good 💛 @nikeyoga #teamnike #NikeWomen

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Radhi Devlukia-Shetty on September 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'You to don't have have that last conversation, send that final message or prove you were right. The resolution isn't always found through the noise of endless words back and forth, it can be found through the subtle moments of silence. Don't lose your power waiting for closure to be given to you when you can giveitittoyourself Radhi'.

node.text: You can do more than you think. Don't underestimate your power to heal yourself 💛 #quotes #quotestoliveby
